ATLANTEAN NOMAD: Wandering tattooed dimension-walker

A True Atlantean who wanders the megaverse trading, exploring, and
fighting the forces of the Splugorth. One of the most versatile
dimension-walkers on Rifts Earth, the Nomad combines magical tattoo
power with broad survival skills.

Atlantean Nomads carry magical tattoos from birth. Their PPE pool fuels
tattoo activation. They are trained in dimensional navigation, multiple
languages, and lore of Rifts and magic. Skill picks come from Physical,
Technical, Wilderness, and Rogue categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Race restriction: Atlantean only.
  Attribute requirements: None.
  PPE: Starting pool (base PPE + ME bonus) grows each level.
  Equipment: Enchanted Atlantean armor, a short sword with at least one
    magic tattoo weapon effect, dimensional compass, and survival gear.

